{
  "title": "ISic000190. Funerary plaque for Lesbius and Damophilus",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag, Alex Antoniou</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Publi\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Publi\">P̣(ubli)</span></span> · <span data-text=\"liberto\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">l(iberto)</span> · <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Lesbi o\"><span data-text=\"Lesbi\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">Lesbi</span>  <span data-text=\"o\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"\">[o]</span></span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"liberto\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"\">ḷ(iberto)</span> · <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Damop h ilo\"><span data-text=\"Damop\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"\">Damop</span>  <span data-text=\"h\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"\">ḥ</span>  <span data-text=\"ilo\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"\">[ilo]</span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"tas\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"\">ṭas</span> · <span data-text=\"fecit\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"\">f(ecit)</span> · <span data-text=\"de\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"\">d(e)</span> · <span data-text=\"suo\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"\">s(uo)</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag, Alex Antoniou</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Publi\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Publi\">.</span></span>·<span data-text=\"liberto\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">L</span>·<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Lesbi o\"><span data-text=\"Lesbi\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">LESBI</span><span data-text=\"o\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"\">[.]</span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"liberto\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"\">.</span>·<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Damop h ilo\"><span data-text=\"Damop\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"\">DAMOP</span><span data-text=\"h\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"\">.</span><span data-text=\"ilo\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"\">[...]</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"tas\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"\">.AS</span>·<span data-text=\"fecit\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"\">F</span>·<span data-text=\"de\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"\">D</span>·<span data-text=\"suo\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"\">S</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic000190_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-05\" src=\"ISic000190_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000190.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-05\" src=\"ISic000190-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic000190_rear_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-05\" src=\"ISic000190_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000190_rear.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-05\" src=\"ISic000190_rear-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text based on autopsy</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou</a></p>  <p>[...] To [...] Lesbius, freedman of Publius [..., and ...] Damophilus, freedman of [..., ?] made [this] from his own resources.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>It is clear that lines 1-2 address the dedicatees, both freedmen, but that line 3 would have included the name of the dedicant. The cognomen Lesbius, of Greek origin, is common. The cognomen Damophilus, also of Greek origin, is less common but nonetheless elsewhere attested in the empire.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> VIII 706 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002649\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002649</a>  </li><li> Salinas NSA 1886 337 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a>  </li><li> Bivona 1994 112 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Text is relatively regular and neat, although stonecarver was not able to achieve straight lines on all letters (for instance, the wobbly 'D' in line 2). Serifs used on all letters. The cross-bar on the As are barely noticeable.</p> Line 1  39-42  Line 2  41-42  Line 3  36-38  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
